  "text": "The results of present study indicate that the cognitively normal elderly population had more exercise habit than the group with MCI. These results were consistent with those of previous studies, which found that waking, running, dancing, Tai chi or other physical activities may have effect in decreasing the probabilities of developing MCI [CITATION_1] .",
